		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Michael McColly</span></strong> teaches creative nonfiction at Northwestern University and Columbia College Chicago. He is the author of <em>The After-Death Room: Journey into Spiritual Activism</em>, which chronicles his reporting on <span class="smallcaps">AIDS</span> activism in Africa, Asia, and America. He is currently at work on a book about urban walking.</p><a href="/contributors/michael-mccolly" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
